title: Quick Start Guide - Home Heating Survey
author: AI Agent Team
content:
This is a simple text document in JSON format.

How to Use:
1. Upload documents via the document manager
2. Process them to extract text and structure
3. Search across all your documents
4. Export as structured JSON

Benefits of JSON Upload:
- No PDF parsing needed
- Pre-structured data
- Fast processing
- Easy to generate programmatically

For more information, see the documentation at /PARSER_README.md
